  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc6\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The death of the young man comes from the selfie",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Haldummulla police say that a young man who tried to take a selfie fell down from the waterfall near the foot of the mountain in Leiban section of Haldummulla Udaveriya estate and died.",
        "The deceased was a 24-year-old youth named Madhusankha Sagara who resided in Welimada Guruthalawa.",
        "He was visiting this waterfall with three friends when he met with this accident.",
        "When he was taking a selfie, he slipped and fell down the waterfall and his body was found in a waterhole about two hundred meters below."
      ],
